episodes.title: 3 days in Dimona: African Hebrew Israelites (Part 1)
episodes.description: South African film director, Tarryn Crossman of Black Rage Productions, travels to Israel to meet a group of African Americans who trace their routes back to the original Hebrews and who have settled in 'the Holy Land'.
